msgid "RACE_HUMAN_NAME"
msgstr "Human"

msgid "RACE_HUMAN_DESC"
msgstr "You are an ordinary human."

msgid "RACE_HUMAN_BEHAVIOR_DESC"
msgstr "Humans have no yao instinct constraint; their actions are mainly shaped by personality, objectives, sect, alignment, and current circumstances."

msgid "RACE_FOX_NAME"
msgstr "Fox Yao"

msgid "RACE_FOX_DESC"
msgstr "Fox yao are naturally clever, skilled at reading expressions and moods, often striking in appearance, and commonly seen as having an innate affinity for opportunity and social ties."

msgid "RACE_FOX_BEHAVIOR_DESC"
msgstr "Fox yao actions should first show reading moods, social probing, advantageous trades, and a nose for opportunity. Ordinary personality may only shape the method; it must not turn fox yao into blunt cultivators who do not cultivate relationships."

msgid "RACE_WOLF_NAME"
msgstr "Wolf Yao"

msgid "RACE_WOLF_DESC"
msgstr "Wolf yao have strong bloodlines, value survival, hunting, and battle, possess keen instincts and swift movement, and often temper their cultivation through combat."

msgid "RACE_WOLF_BEHAVIOR_DESC"
msgstr "Wolf yao actions should first show survival, hunting, combat, territory, and judgments of strength. Ordinary personality may only change how they attack; it must not make wolf yao sit in idle discourse for long or avoid all conflict."

msgid "RACE_BIRD_NAME"
msgstr "Bird Yao"

msgid "RACE_BIRD_DESC"
msgstr "Bird yao have broad perception and nimble movement, are born to yearn for distant places, and excel at scouting, escape, and exploring the unknown."

msgid "RACE_BIRD_BEHAVIOR_DESC"
msgstr "Bird yao actions should first show migration, scouting, travel, observation, and evasion. Ordinary personality may only affect route and pace; it must not leave bird yao trapped in one place without cause or abandoning their need for wider sight."

msgid "RACE_SNAKE_NAME"
msgstr "Snake Yao"

msgid "RACE_SNAKE_DESC"
msgstr "Snake yao have subtle auras and patient ways, excel at hiding and ambush, are often feared by human cultivators, and adapt well to dark and dangerous places."

msgid "RACE_SNAKE_BEHAVIOR_DESC"
msgstr "Snake yao actions should first show lurking, patience, probing, indirect routes, and sudden ambush. Ordinary personality may only change how ruthless they are; it must not make snake yao into loud, frontal, openly bustling cultivators."

msgid "RACE_TURTLE_NAME"
msgstr "Turtle Yao"

msgid "RACE_TURTLE_DESC"
msgstr "Turtle yao are long-lived and steady of body, slow and cautious in conduct, and most skilled at defense, recuperation, and long secluded cultivation."

msgid "RACE_TURTLE_BEHAVIOR_DESC"
msgstr "Turtle yao actions should first show slowness, defense, recuperation, rest, and seclusion. Unless avoiding danger, breaking through, fulfilling sect duties, pursuing a clear target, or meeting resource needs, they should not move frequently or initiate conflict; ordinary personality must not override this guarding instinct."
